Detailed Description

This object outputs StateActionModel objects given a Planner object (and the policy it implies) as input.

This computation completes the recursive composition of child StateActionModel objects first into an MDP, then into a policy, and now into the model of an abstract action that corresponds to achieving the goal function given to the Planner object, using the child actions.
